{
  "name": "RPlog_A_Smuggler_Walks_Into_a_Bar_Part_2",
  "title": "A Smuggler Walks Into a Bar (Part 2)",
  "summary": "On Bothawui, the pirate captain Vane and her crew lie low in a scrubby ditch with the smuggler Jaspar and the Twi'lek Ka'una, planning a raid to recover Jaspar's impounded ship from a heavily guarded lot. Ka, the reluctant demolitions hand, takes a satchel of detonite charges and slips off through the shadows to blow the impound lot's fences and floodlights while Jaspar scouts the target and Vane readies the assault. When the muffled charges plunge the lot into darkness, Jaspar dashes to his ship and frantically works the controls to get it operational, but a metallic echo blows their cover and Vane bellows the order to open fire. A chaotic firefight erupts between the pirates and the station guards as Jaspar coaxes his old ship's engines roaring to life, takes a well-aimed shot at a guard, and the crew piles aboard. With Imperial interceptors faster than their freighter closing in, the battered ship lifts off, weapons arming, as the heist tips into a desperate escape.",
